{"tid":429699,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳健波指會以主席指引修訂會議程序","createTime":"2017-10-09T06:59:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T14:00:31.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fafe49f6fc4196407e1cca7beed8ead70cb0bf59","tid":429699,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T06:59:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">陳健波指會以主席指引修訂會議程序</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】立法會財委會主席陳健波表示，建制派將會就會議程序提出修訂，並且已準備好文件，部分可以透過主席指引落實，不需取得議員同意。<br />\n<br />\n陳健波將會與立法會秘書處一同約見民主派議員解釋修訂。<br />\n<br />\n兩項可以透過主席指引落實的修訂包括釐清會議時間、被逐離場議員不能重返會議。另外，議員動議縮短表決鐘聲後，每名議員的額外發言時間會由三分鐘減至一分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=238720\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D238720&d=YCODDMybYN7foeKrmTtIoZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=b4706da3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D238720&h=7485c859\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=238720</a>"},{"pid":"a36628babf99af36fd8b34d8b806ec8ed0306276","tid":429699,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T07:02:31.000Z","msg":"直接改非親共議員唔比發言啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975bc5095a7d86ba77345b989bdf33c7ad975cc1","tid":429699,"uid":63779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:54:33.000Z","msg":"佢真係想玩點人數點到樣樣過唔到?"},{"pid":"1c149ff8303afb4c2b84e43091e8e09ffc34a39e","tid":429699,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:56:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直接改非親共議員唔比發言啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直接捉去坐監啦，仲俾佢地入去搞搞震咩"},{"pid":"7c718572f5f8afdad08af21a82905ffbdb70a764","tid":429699,"uid":78522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:58:03.000Z","ms